<P>Come and Welcome TO <HI>Je&s;us Chri&s;t.</HI> Or, a Plain and Profitable DISCOURSE On <HI>John</HI> VI. Ver&s;e xxxvii. SHEWING, The Cau&s;e, Truth and Manner of the Coming of a <HI>Sinner to JES&V;S CHRIST</HI>; with his Happy Recep|tion, and Ble&s;&s;ed Entertainment.</P>
<P>Written by <HI>JOHN B&V;NYAN,</HI> Author of <HI>the Pilgrim</HI>'s <HI>Progre&s;s.</HI></P>
<Q><P>And they &s;hall come which were ready to Pari&s;h,</P>
<BIBL><HI>I&s;aiah xxvii. 13.</HI></BIBL></Q>
<P><HI>The Twelfth Edition.</HI></P>
<P>BOSTON, Reprinted, and are to be &s;old at the BIBLE in <HI>Cornhill.</HI> 1728.</P>
