<P>That none can &s;ave but <HI>Je&s;us Chri&s;t,</HI> is evident from <HI>Acts</HI> 4.12. Neither is there Salvation in any other; and he hath given us Eternal Life, &amp; this Life is in his Son. If Life could have been had any where el&s;e it &s;hould have been in the Law, no man living &s;hall be ju&s;tified; and i<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter"> not ju&s;tified, then no Life.</P>
