<P>Thirdly, It mu&s;t be by Je&s;us Chri&s;t, that Life <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">ight be at God's di&s;po&s;e who hath great Pity for <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">he Poor, the Lowly, the Meek, the Broken in heart, <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">nd for them that others care not for, <HI>P&s;al.</HI> 34 6.</P>
